reviewText: Not good for me I will try another.

This is a fantastic help to anyone who wants to learn these songs!  I said four stars rather than five because I wish it had a tab sheet enclosed and you could change the intro lesson view to rightside up as though you were looking at a player in front of you; however don't let that stop you from buying.  This is a great DVD loaded with usable techniques for rock and blues
I definitely would buy another one thank you
Grat video for intermediate player. Wonderful opportunity to experience Blues Rock roots.
